## External Triggers (外部触发)

### 3.1 Webhook 机制详解

OpenClaw Gateway 提供 HTTP Webhook 端点用于外部触发。

**启用配置**:
```json5
{
  hooks: {
    enabled: true,
    token: "your-secure-token",      // 必需
    path: "/hooks",                   // 默认路径
    allowedAgentIds: ["main", "hooks"], // 允许的 Agent ID
    defaultSessionKey: "hook:ingress",
    allowRequestSessionKey: false,    // 是否允许请求指定 sessionKey
    allowedSessionKeyPrefixes: ["hook:"]
  }
}
```

**认证方式**:
- Header: `Authorization: Bearer <token>` (推荐)
- Header: `x-openclaw-token: <token>`
- Query string tokens 被拒绝 (返回 400)

### 3.2 Webhook 端点

#### 3.2.1 POST /hooks/wake

触发心跳事件。

**请求体**:
```json
{
  "text": "系统事件描述",
  "mode": "now" | "next-heartbeat"
}
```

**示例**:
```bash
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18789/hooks/wake \
  -H 'Authorization: Bearer SECRET' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{"text":"新邮件到达","mode":"now"}'
```

#### 3.2.2 POST /hooks/agent

运行独立的 Agent 任务。

**请求体**:
```json
{
  "message": "任务描述",
  "name": "任务名称",
  "agentId": "目标 Agent",
  "sessionKey": "session 标识",
  "wakeMode": "now" | "next-heartbeat",
  "deliver": true,
  "channel": "whatsapp" | "telegram" | "discord" | ...,
  "to": "接收者",
  "model": "模型覆盖",
  "thinking": "思考级别",
  "timeoutSeconds": 120
}
```

**示例**:
```bash
curl -X POST http://127.0.0.1:18789/hooks/agent \
  -H 'Authorization: Bearer SECRET' \
  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \
  -d '{
    "message": "总结收件箱",
    "name": "Email",
    "agentId": "main",
    "deliver": true,
    "channel": "telegram",
    "to": "123456789"
  }'
```

### 3.3 Feishu 集成

Feishu 通过 WebSocket 长连接接收事件，无需公开 Webhook URL。

**配置**:
```json5
{
  channels: {
    feishu: {
      enabled: true,
      dmPolicy: "pairing",
      accounts: {
        main: {
          appId: "cli_xxx",
          appSecret: "xxx",
          botName: "My AI Assistant"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

**多 Agent 路由**:
```json5
{
  agents: {
    list: [
      { id: "main" },
      { id: "work", workspace: "~/.openclaw/workspace-work" },
      { id: "family", workspace: "~/.openclaw/workspace-family" }
    ]
  },
  bindings: [
    {
      agentId: "main",
      match: { channel: "feishu", peer: { kind: "direct", id: "ou_xxx" } }
    },
    {
      agentId: "work",
      match: { channel: "feishu", peer: { kind: "group", id: "oc_yyy" } }
    }
  ]
}
```

### 3.4 GitHub Webhook 集成

**方案 1: 直接映射到 /hooks/agent**

```bash
# GitHub Webhook URL
http://your-gateway:18789/hooks/agent
```

**请求体转换** (通过 hooks.mappings):
```json5
{
  hooks: {
    mappings: {
      github: {
        match: { source: "github" },
        action: "agent",
        payload: {
          message: "GitHub 事件: ${{event}} - ${{repository}}",
          name: "GitHub",
          deliver: true,
          channel: "telegram"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

**方案 2: 自定义转换脚本**
```json5
{
  hooks: {
    transformsDir: "~/.openclaw/hooks/transforms",
    mappings: {
      github: {
        match: { headers: { "X-GitHub-Event": "*" } },
        transform: {
          module: "github-transform.js"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

**github-transform.js**:
```javascript
module.exports = function transform(payload, context) {
  const event = context.headers["X-GitHub-Event"];

  switch (event) {
    case "push":
      return {
        message: `代码推送: ${payload.repository.name}\n提交: ${payload.head_commit.message}`,
        name: "GitHub Push",
        agentId: "main",
        deliver: true,
        channel: "telegram",
        to: "your-chat-id"
      };

    case "pull_request":
      return {
        message: `PR ${payload.action}: ${payload.pull_request.title}\n${payload.pull_request.html_url}`,
        name: "GitHub PR",
        deliver: true
      };

    default:
      return {
        message: `GitHub 事件: ${event}`,
        name: "GitHub"
      };
  }
};
```

